## Root words

### Part two of root words

### [Part 1](/post/part1)

### [Part 3](/post/part3)

#### dict

* Latin "To write"
  - dictation
  - predict
  - dictator

#### tele

* Greek "over long distances"
  - telephone
  - television
  - telegraph

#### pict

* Greek "To draw or to show visually"
  - picture
  - pictograph
  - picturesque

#### ridi/risi

* Latin "To laugh or to mock"
  - ridiculous
  - deride
  - derisive

#### para

* Greek "beyond, beside"
  - paranormal
  - parallel
  - paramedic

#### que/qui

* Latin "to ask or to seek"
  - question
  - request
  - inquire
